lead_paragraph: Kentucky moves into the No. 1 spot in The Associated Press college basketball poll, replacing Duke, which dropped to sixth following its final-seconds loss to Kansas in the Champions Classic.

headline.print_headline: Kentucky Takes Over No. 1 Spot From Duke in Basketball Poll
